1
00:00:47,040 --> 00:00:48,770
Ah, it wasn't me, Your Majesty.

2
00:00:49,480 --> 00:00:51,080
It was those two young eunuchs.

3
00:00:51,080 --> 00:00:52,940
I will kill them for Your Majesty.

4
00:00:53,560 --> 00:00:54,240
Aunt.

5
00:00:54,840 --> 00:00:58,100
The people you planted are getting more and more insolent.

6
00:00:58,840 --> 00:01:01,640
Now is not the time to kill this dog.

7
00:01:03,360 --> 00:01:03,890
Alright.

8
00:01:05,760 --> 00:01:07,960
Sun Liang failed to manage his subordinates properly.

9
00:01:07,960 --> 00:01:09,200
He will be fined half a year's salary.

10
00:01:09,200 --> 00:01:09,720
Yes.

11
00:01:10,760 --> 00:01:12,280
I'll go kill them right now.

12
00:01:12,280 --> 00:01:13,140
Get out of here!

13
00:01:15,800 --> 00:01:17,480
Go.

14
00:01:21,080 --> 00:01:21,960
Useless.

15
00:01:24,200 --> 00:01:26,060
Ayan, don't be afraid. It's okay.

16
00:01:28,760 --> 00:01:31,680
How can a mere eunuch like you protect him?

17
00:01:31,680 --> 00:01:32,800
His Majesty gave the young prince the largest

18
00:01:32,800 --> 00:01:35,880
and best palace in the palace.

19
00:01:36,200 --> 00:01:37,840
They will still bully him.

20
00:01:39,000 --> 00:01:40,759
Knowing it was Eunuch Sun,

21
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:42,729
but not killing him on the spot.

22
00:01:43,400 --> 00:01:46,460
Does Si Xingxuan have some unspeakable difficulties?

23
00:01:47,160 --> 00:01:48,960
It seems I have to think of a way.

24
00:01:50,080 --> 00:01:51,960
The royal doctor said the young prince was poisoned.

25
00:01:51,960 --> 00:01:53,600
The fever will go down

26
00:01:53,600 --> 00:01:56,729
only when the toxin is completely cleared from the body.

27
00:01:57,960 --> 00:01:59,759
How dare he bully Ayan like this.

28
00:02:01,040 --> 00:02:02,760
I am not dead yet.

29
00:02:03,200 --> 00:02:04,000
Your Majesty.

30
00:02:04,680 --> 00:02:07,280
I hope you will protect Ayan well in the future.

31
00:02:10,199 --> 00:02:11,730
I don't mean anything else.

32
00:02:13,200 --> 00:02:14,480
Just a reminder.

33
00:02:18,560 --> 00:02:19,820
Take good care of Ayan.

34
00:02:31,680 --> 00:02:35,160
I feel His Majesty actually cares a lot about the little prince.

35
00:02:35,160 --> 00:02:36,560
What's the use of caring?

36
00:02:37,360 --> 00:02:39,290
Now that the little prince is sick,

37
00:02:39,400 --> 00:02:41,400
he doesn't even dare to visit often.

38
00:02:41,560 --> 00:02:43,000
If he visits too much,

39
00:02:43,360 --> 00:02:44,960
it will become his weakness.

40
00:02:45,960 --> 00:02:49,600
The Grand Princess is no good.

41
00:02:50,640 --> 00:02:51,880
But at that time,

42
00:02:51,880 --> 00:02:53,079
why did you lie to me

43
00:02:53,079 --> 00:02:55,140
and say that Si Xingxuan was a tyrant?

44
00:02:57,280 --> 00:02:59,600
You sneaked into the palace in a wooden barrel.

45
00:02:59,600 --> 00:03:00,960
How could I trust you?

46
00:03:01,920 --> 00:03:02,880
All right.

47
00:03:03,680 --> 00:03:05,640
Uh, I have another question.

48
00:03:06,560 --> 00:03:09,220
Why doesn't His Majesty dare to touch Eunuch Sun

49
00:03:09,560 --> 00:03:11,960
when he is the Emperor?

50
00:03:12,440 --> 00:03:14,640
Because he is the Grand Princess's man.

51
00:03:15,280 --> 00:03:16,440
Once he is killed,

52
00:03:17,760 --> 00:03:21,079
the Grand Princess will take vicious revenge on the little prince.

53
00:03:21,079 --> 00:03:23,880
That woman is just too crazy.

54
00:03:24,560 --> 00:03:25,960
What a lunatic.

55
00:03:26,400 --> 00:03:27,930
His Majesty is in a bad mood.

56
00:03:28,040 --> 00:03:29,170
I'll go check on him.

57
00:03:35,600 --> 00:03:36,640
After so long,

58
00:03:37,760 --> 00:03:39,290
there's finally some hope.

59
00:03:41,280 --> 00:03:42,079
Cang Yue,

60
00:03:43,560 --> 00:03:45,240
please don't let me down.

61
00:03:50,880 --> 00:03:52,040
Come and sit.

62
00:03:56,800 --> 00:03:58,200
I told you to come and sit.

63
00:04:01,400 --> 00:04:02,800
Thank you, Your Majesty.

64
00:04:14,600 --> 00:04:16,279
You saw it yourself today.

65
00:04:17,360 --> 00:04:18,519
In this deep palace,

66
00:04:19,440 --> 00:04:20,899
danger lurks everywhere.

67
00:04:21,200 --> 00:04:22,930
You should leave immediately.

68
00:04:24,080 --> 00:04:26,610
I am not afraid of being dragged into trouble.

69
00:04:26,760 --> 00:04:28,360
I just want to know

70
00:04:28,360 --> 00:04:31,220
the truth behind the massacre of the Yueying Tribe.

71
00:04:35,480 --> 00:04:36,360
I promise you

72
00:04:37,600 --> 00:04:39,260
I will help you find the truth.

73
00:04:43,200 --> 00:04:44,400
You don't believe me.

74
00:04:52,560 --> 00:04:53,360
That's true.

75
00:04:55,840 --> 00:04:58,370
I can't even deal with a eunuch like Sun Liang.

76
00:04:59,280 --> 00:05:00,720
Who says you can't?

77
00:05:03,560 --> 00:05:06,080
Evil will be punished by evil.

78
00:05:07,000 --> 00:05:09,280
So I won't leave the palace.

79
00:05:09,280 --> 00:05:10,340
But from what I see,

80
00:05:10,800 --> 00:05:13,200
evil people in this deep palace

81
00:05:13,200 --> 00:05:14,000
can thrive.

82
00:05:14,000 --> 00:05:16,760
Greedy people always have weaknesses.

83
00:05:22,000 --> 00:05:23,800
I don't want to leave the palace.

84
00:05:24,880 --> 00:05:27,840
I just want to go to the riverbank with Your Majesty

85
00:05:28,760 --> 00:05:30,820
and fish in the clear water together.

86
00:05:34,280 --> 00:05:37,560
Experiencer's character task goal is 40% complete.

87
00:05:40,760 --> 00:05:43,360
Does Your Majesty know how to fish?

88
00:05:44,200 --> 00:05:45,000
Fishing?

89
00:05:49,680 --> 00:05:50,760
Lady Cangyue.

90
00:05:58,200 --> 00:05:59,560
About yesterday,

91
00:05:59,760 --> 00:06:01,680
I never intended to kill you.

92
00:06:03,040 --> 00:06:03,960
Really?

93
00:06:05,680 --> 00:06:07,480
Why do I feel

94
00:06:07,480 --> 00:06:09,210
it's because you were too slow?

95
00:06:09,600 --> 00:06:10,200
No, no, no.

96
00:06:10,880 --> 00:06:13,360
Every maid His Majesty favors

97
00:06:13,360 --> 00:06:16,800
has to go through this process with me.

98
00:06:28,760 --> 00:06:31,760
You have passed this process.

99
00:06:43,159 --> 00:06:44,020
Anything else?

100
00:06:44,159 --> 00:06:45,600
No, nothing.

101
00:06:47,120 --> 00:06:49,840
Then things between us

102
00:06:50,159 --> 00:06:51,360
are settled.

103
00:06:51,760 --> 00:06:52,800
We'll be at peace.

104
00:06:52,800 --> 00:06:53,120
Mm.

105
00:07:10,160 --> 00:07:12,680
The show has just begun. Just wait.

106
00:07:15,640 --> 00:07:17,040
Hey, did you know?

107
00:07:17,200 --> 00:07:19,200
His Majesty is exclusively favoring a maid now.

108
00:07:19,200 --> 00:07:20,400
It's that Cangyue.

109
00:07:20,400 --> 00:07:22,160
She has completely captivated His Majesty.

110
00:07:22,160 --> 00:07:23,600
Why still call her a maid?

111
00:07:23,600 --> 00:07:26,460
Next time we see her, we'll have to call her Consort.

112
00:07:26,480 --> 00:07:27,840
We are all human, but with different fates.

113
00:07:27,840 --> 00:07:29,240
We are all maids.

114
00:07:29,240 --> 00:07:31,900
Why does she get His Majesty's exclusive favor?

115
00:07:33,440 --> 00:07:35,360
My figure isn't bad either.

116
00:07:36,280 --> 00:07:37,880
Let's get back to work.

117
00:07:37,880 --> 00:07:40,480
Head Eunuch Sun will punish us if he catches us.

118
00:07:46,880 --> 00:07:50,280
You have been paying your respects quite frequently lately.

119
00:07:55,159 --> 00:07:57,480
My father and I are where we are today

120
00:07:57,640 --> 00:07:59,300
all thanks to Aunt's support.

121
00:07:59,640 --> 00:08:01,400
I am truly grateful,

122
00:08:01,400 --> 00:08:04,080
so naturally I care about you, Princess.

123
00:08:04,480 --> 00:08:08,160
Yes, I have always been thinking of you.

124
00:08:10,360 --> 00:08:11,640
I think

125
00:08:12,320 --> 00:08:15,240
you fail to capture His Majesty's heart

126
00:08:15,240 --> 00:08:17,200
and have nothing better to do.

127
00:08:20,880 --> 00:08:22,880
Having been concubines for so long,

128
00:08:23,840 --> 00:08:25,900
have any of you ever served him in bed?

129
00:08:31,720 --> 00:08:33,960
What use are you?

130
00:08:33,960 --> 00:08:36,559
Every one of you holds the title of concubine.

131
00:08:36,559 --> 00:08:39,220
Yet you can't even capture the Emperor's heart.

132
00:08:39,480 --> 00:08:41,840
You are worse than a lowly palace maid.

133
00:08:45,560 --> 00:08:46,890
I don't need to teach you

134
00:08:48,080 --> 00:08:50,880
what to do, do I?

135
00:08:55,640 --> 00:08:58,360
- You may leave.
- Yes.

136
00:09:14,160 --> 00:09:15,890
At such an important occasion,

137
00:09:16,040 --> 00:09:18,570
that little palace maid is nowhere to be seen.

138
00:09:18,960 --> 00:09:20,760
Has she fallen out of favor?

139
00:09:22,560 --> 00:09:24,880
I thought a real seductress had appeared

140
00:09:24,880 --> 00:09:26,680
and stolen His Majesty's heart.

141
00:09:26,760 --> 00:09:29,360
It seems Cangyue is nothing special after all.

142
00:09:29,600 --> 00:09:31,360
His Majesty is hosting a banquet today.

143
00:09:31,360 --> 00:09:32,440
He must miss us.

144
00:09:35,800 --> 00:09:37,360
Your Majesty.

145
00:09:46,080 --> 00:09:49,200
Your Majesty, I...

146
00:09:51,160 --> 00:09:52,800
If your eyes are uncomfortable,

147
00:09:52,800 --> 00:09:55,200
summon the imperial physician to take a look.

148
00:09:55,200 --> 00:09:58,480
Your Majesty, you haven't visited me for a long time.

149
00:10:01,160 --> 00:10:02,420
I have face blindness.

150
00:10:03,160 --> 00:10:03,960
I can't see.

151
00:10:04,760 --> 00:10:07,120
Your Majesty, in my palace...

152
00:10:07,320 --> 00:10:08,760
I told you not to talk nonsense.

153
00:10:08,760 --> 00:10:09,720
Your Majesty,

154
00:10:10,120 --> 00:10:12,960
I have the best pre-Qingming Longjing tea in my palace.

155
00:10:12,960 --> 00:10:14,480
I would like you to taste it.

156
00:10:14,480 --> 00:10:16,040
What's so good about your tea?

157
00:10:16,040 --> 00:10:17,960
Your Majesty, I have a silver heron.

158
00:10:17,960 --> 00:10:18,800
It's so cute.

159
00:10:18,800 --> 00:10:20,200
Come to my place to see it.

160
00:10:20,640 --> 00:10:21,880
What's the rush?

161
00:10:21,880 --> 00:10:24,540
If His Majesty goes anywhere, he will come to me.

162
00:10:26,800 --> 00:10:27,640
Your Majesty,

163
00:10:27,920 --> 00:10:29,580
it's time to flip the name tag.

164
00:10:39,360 --> 00:10:40,520
Consort Yu.

165
00:10:41,720 --> 00:10:42,760
Ah, it's me.

166
00:10:42,760 --> 00:10:44,240
Your Majesty, I...

167
00:10:44,240 --> 00:10:44,800
Get out.

168
00:10:45,080 --> 00:10:45,520
Ah.

169
00:10:45,680 --> 00:10:46,920
I told you to get out.

170
00:10:47,400 --> 00:10:48,280
Hmph. I don't care.

171
00:10:48,280 --> 00:10:49,280
I am staying right here.

172
00:10:49,280 --> 00:10:49,760
Hmph.

173
00:10:50,560 --> 00:10:51,080
I am staying right here.

174
00:10:51,080 --> 00:10:52,200
You... shut up.

175
00:10:59,280 --> 00:11:00,600
Consort Hua.

176
00:11:00,600 --> 00:11:01,440
Thank you, Your Majesty.

177
00:11:01,440 --> 00:11:02,400
You get out too.

178
00:11:04,360 --> 00:11:05,160
If she won't get out,

179
00:11:05,160 --> 00:11:06,020
neither will I.

180
00:11:07,560 --> 00:11:08,840
Your Majesty.
